        "text_UFbQpn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Cook & Bathe, we offer a carefully curated selection of premium kitchen products to help you build the kitchen you’ve always envisioned. From high-performance appliances to designer tapware and durable kitchen sinks, our collections blend timeless style with everyday functionality - perfect for any home and every kitchen aesthetic.</p>"
