    "image_with_text_iqYei4": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_bCdP6d": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Tapware: The Finishing Touch",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_4CniKG": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Enhance your kitchen with high-quality tapware that combines sophisticated design with exceptional performance. At Cook & Bathe, we offer an extensive range of kitchen tapware to suit every style and functionality need. Choose from pull-out kitchen taps, gooseneck mixers, and single-lever sink mixers in modern finishes including brushed gold, matte black, chrome, and brushed nickel.</p><p>Our kitchen tapware collection features top-tier brands known for durability, innovation, and design excellence:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/phoenix-kitchen-tapware\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/phoenix-kitchen-tapware\">Phoenix Tapware</a><strong> </strong>– Elegant, durable kitchen tapware crafted for Australian homes<br/></p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/franke-tapware\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/franke-tapware\">Franke</a> – Sleek, innovative sink mixers blending style and practicality</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/hansgrohe-sink-mixers\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/hansgrohe-sink-mixers\">Hansgrohe</a> – German-engineered tapware offering cutting-edge design and water-saving features</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/ikon\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/ikon\">Ikon</a> – Contemporary tapware solutions designed for performance and visual impact</p><p>Whether you’re completing a renovation or upgrading your current fixtures, our tapware range delivers the perfect balance of aesthetic appeal and water efficiency. </p><p>Explore the full collection and find the ideal tapware to complete your kitchen.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
