    "image_with_text_7aJNMr": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_N7jMRJ": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Appliances: Elevate Your Kitchen",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_rE3kzK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Upgrade your kitchen with Cook & Bathe’s expertly curated range of kitchen appliances, designed to enhance your cooking, cooling, and cleaning experience. Our collection includes high-performance <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/ovens\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/ovens\">ovens</a>, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/cooktopsf\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/cooktopsf\">cooktops</a>, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fridges-kitchen\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fridges-kitchen\">fridges</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/dishwashers\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/dishwashers\">dishwashers</a> from trusted brands such as Smeg, Euro Appliances, and Kleenmaid - renowned for their energy efficiency, innovative technology, and stylish finishes.</p><p>Discover our range of kitchen appliances and enjoy seamless functionality in every corner of your kitchen:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/ovens\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/ovens\">Electric</a>, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/pyrolytic-ovens\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/pyrolytic-ovens\">pyrolytic</a>, and steam ovens built for precise and consistent baking results</li><li>Choose from <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/gas-cooktops-stove\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/gas-cooktops-stove\">gas cooktops</a>, <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/induction\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/induction\">induction cooktops</a>, or ceramic models for superior heat control</li><li>Energy-efficient and whisper-quiet dishwashers for effortless, eco-conscious cleaning</li><li>A wide selection of <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/freestanding-fridges\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/freestanding-fridges\">freestanding</a> and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/integrated-fridges\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/integrated-fridges\">integrated fridges</a> to suit all kitchen sizes and layouts</li></ul><p>Whether you’re completing a full kitchen renovation or upgrading your appliances, our appliance range offers performance, reliability, and design to match every Australian home.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
