    "image_with_text_JbW7Eb": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_BwYxBM": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Rangehoods: Stylish Ventilation Solutions",
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_A39YkN": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Maintain a clean, odour-free kitchen with Cook & Bathe’s premium selection of kitchen rangehoods. Designed to suit a wide variety of kitchen layouts and aesthetics, our collection includes undermount rangehoods, wall-mounted rangehoods, and ceiling-mounted rangehoods that deliver powerful ventilation with quiet performance.</p><p>Whether you’re after a minimalist look or a bold statement piece, our rangehoods offer the perfect balance of function and form. Engineered for modern Australian kitchens, they efficiently remove smoke, steam, and odours while complementing your cooking appliances.</p><p>Explore our top brands:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/smeg-rangehoods\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/smeg-rangehoods\">Smeg</a> – Sleek Italian-designed rangehoods that blend elegance with advanced performance</li><li><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/euro-appliances-rangehoods\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/euro-appliances-rangehoods\">Euro Appliances</a> – Quiet, powerful ventilation systems for everyday cooking</li><li><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/kleenmaid-rangehoods\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/kleenmaid-rangehoods\">Kleenmaid</a> – Stylish and functional designs ideal for contemporary kitchens</li></ul><p>Upgrade your kitchen today with a high-performance rangehood that enhances both air quality and visual appeal.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
